<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Message - Artium</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f7f9fc;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      padding: 30px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #007bff;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .message-box {
      background-color: #f0f4f8;
      border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .message-sender {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #007bff;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .message-content {
      color: #555;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .action-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .action-button:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>New Message</h1>

    <p>You have received a new message on Artium:</p>

    <div class="message-box">
      <div class="message-sender">From: {{senderName}}</div>
      <div class="message-content">"{{messageContent}}"</div>
    </div>

    <p>Click the button below to view and reply:</p>

    <a href="https://artium.com/messages/{{conversationId}}" class="action-button">View Message</a>

    <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">
      You're receiving this email because you have notifications enabled for messages on Artium. 
      <a href="https://artium.com/settings/notifications">Manage your notification preferences</a>
    </p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Artium Team</p>
      <p><a href="https://artium.com">https://artium.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
